            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蓝骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 14:00:35 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Borderlands 4]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Civilization VII]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Mafia: The Old Country]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[TGA 2024]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Witcher 4]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1281327</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>在今日举行的 2024 年游戏大奖（The Game Awards）中，除了让人回顾今年的优秀游戏外，游戏厂商也趁机会公布大作，其中《巫师》、《边缘禁地》、《四海兄弟》和《文明帝国》的最新续作也有全新预告片公开。<br /><span id="more-1281327"></span></p><h2>《巫师 4》(The Witcher 4)</h2><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_51092"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/54dabgZJ5YA?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>今次公开的是《巫师 4》首个预告片，虽然没有实际游戏画面，但也预告了游戏故事内容，预告中主角不再是杰洛特 (Geralt) 而是他的养女希里 (Ciri)，她在偏远村庄接下猎魔士委托，面对需要人类献祭的邪恶生物。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1281335" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/4thegameawards202419-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/4thegameawards202419-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/4thegameawards202419-scaled.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1281336" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/4thegameawards202441-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/4thegameawards202441-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/4thegameawards202441-scaled.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>在村民准备献祭年轻女孩时希里挺身而出，却发现自己陷入与村民的偏见和迷信的冲突中。游戏采用虚幻引擎 5 制作，预计成为系列新三部曲的首作，不过发行时间就尚未公布。</p><h2>《边缘禁地 4》(Borderlands 4)</h2><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_69255"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/R8CaRnf0zO0?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>《边缘禁地 4》预告片则揭露全新反派「时域天尊」(The Timekeeper)，以及最危险星球凯罗星 (Kairos) 上的冒险。游戏将提供传统全新宝库猎人技能树系统，新的探索机制，以及可自由召唤载具的功能。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1281333" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/borderlands4firstloo-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/borderlands4firstloo-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/borderlands4firstloo-scaled.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1281334" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/borderlands4firstloo-1-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/borderlands4firstloo-1-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/borderlands4firstloo-1-scaled.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>制作人 Randy Pitchford 表示，这将是系列最疯狂的作品，提供前所未有的武器系统和难忘的剧情。游戏支援单人游玩或与最多三名玩家合作，预计 2025 年推出。</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
