            <category>
                <![CDATA[艾尔登法环，黑夜君临]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1281302</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>大受欢迎的《艾尔登法环》(Elden Ring) 不论原作和 DLC 都获得很高的评价，今日 FromSoftware 就宣布将会推出衍生作品《艾尔登法环，黑夜君临》，以平行世界为设定，采用协力生存型玩法。<br /><span id="more-1281302"></span></p><p>今次公布的新作《艾尔登法环，黑夜君临》(Elden Ring Nightreign) 是与《艾尔登法环》独立的游戏新作，由《黑暗灵魂》系列资深开发者石崎淳也担任监督而不是原作的宫崎英高。游戏与原作世界观相同，沿用部分来自原作的敌人及武器，不过设定上就不是同一时间线而是平行世界，因此不会影响原作故事内容。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_52720"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/K2DyEf0V-Vw?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>新作不同于原作的动作 RPG 玩法，采用协力生存游戏玩法，支援单人或三人游玩，比起故事更强调战斗体验。玩家需选择不同职业的「渡夜者」角色，在游戏内的三日时间内，在随机地形中探索、成长并对抗强敌。每个角色都拥有独特的「技艺」和「绝活」，如使用特殊匕首或召唤巨大墓碑等能力，提供不同的战术变化。玩家需要在不断缩小的范围内探索、获取装备和符文经验，面对一波波的敌人生存三日，然后合力击败最后的「黑夜王」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1281319" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/03-8-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/03-8-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/03-8.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1281320" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/04-8-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/04-8-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/04-8.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1281321" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/05-6-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/05-6-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/05-6.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>游戏将会在 2025 年全球同步推出，支援 PlayStation 5／PlayStation 4／Xbox Series X|S／Xbox One／STEAM 平台，有兴趣的朋友不妨继续留意进一步的公布。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1281322" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/06-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/06-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/06.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1281323" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/07-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/07-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/07.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1281324" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/08-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/08-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/08.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>来源：新闻稿</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
